data.description: Single story living on desirable Edgewood Dr. with a twist. This spacious Cape Cod offers 4 bedrooms and one and a half baths in just under 2,050 sq. ft. A multi-functional living room with fireplace in combination with a partially separated sun/4 season room in the rear of the home is perfectly setup for entertaining or additional living and/or recreation space. All appliances stay in this spacious kitchen offering plenty of storage and plenty of possibilities for future renovation if you so desire. Never carry those heavy laundry baskets up or downstairs again with this conveniently located laundry room off the kitchen. This space can serve multiple functions with enough room for mudroom storage or additional pantry storage. Down the hall you'll find our updated full bathroom and the three main level carpeted bedrooms. Now here's the twist - the 680 sq. ft of upper level space offers a very creative opportunity for a variety of functions such as additional bedroom usage, crafting/hobbying, or a wellness studio. Bring your creative ideas! Our fully fenced in back yard is directly accessible via the sunroom and is ready for any kids, pets, or simply for outdoor entertaining. The exterior shed stays so make sure Santa brings you all the big toys! This home is perfectly situated with trails/biking access to Baldwin-Wallace University and Grindstone Elementary. Easy access to stores, restaurants and our beautiful Metroparks. Call your agent and make this home yours today!
